{"data":[{"name":"108:1","price":"1. (நபியே!) நிச்சயமாக நாம் உமக்கு ‘கவ்ஸர்' என்னும் நீர் தடாகத்தை கொடுத்திருக்கிறோம்.","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَعۡطَيۡنَٰكَ ٱلۡكَوۡثَرَ","category":["108 (Al-Kawthar)","Al-Kawthar","Surah Al-Kawthar"],"ayahNumber":6205,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"108:2","price":"2. ஆகவே, (அவற்றுக்கு நன்றி செலுத்துவதற்காக) நீர் உமது இறைவனைத் தொழுது, குர்பானி (பலி) கொடுத்து வருவீராக.","arabic":"فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنۡحَرۡ","category":["108 (Al-Kawthar)","Al-Kawthar","Surah Al-Kawthar"],"ayahNumber":6206,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"},{"name":"108:3","price":"3. நிச்சயமாக உமது எதிரிதான் சந்ததியற்றவன்.","arabic":"إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ ٱلۡأَبۡتَرُ","category":["108 (Al-Kawthar)","Al-Kawthar","Surah Al-Kawthar"],"ayahNumber":6207,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta"}],"chapter":["108 (Al-Kawthar)","Al-Kawthar","Surah Al-Kawthar","Chapter Al-Kawthar","Kawthar","Surah Kawthar","Chapter Kawthar","Al Kawthar","Surah Al Kawthar","Chapter Al Kawthar","Surah 108","Chapter 108","Abundance","الكَوْثَر"]}